    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/dfa5e4ba7af94a83147071c9a8df58f8.avif?t=1768212087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras_big/dfa5e4ba7af94a83147071c9a8df58f8.avif?t=1768212087 width=1600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/2dc8f1e64b6f1b074b4f09299012ae3c.poster.avif?t=1768212087\" width=954 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/2dc8f1e64b6f1b074b4f09299012ae3c.webm?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/2dc8f1e64b6f1b074b4f09299012ae3c.mp4?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《It's Breaking Out》</strong>是一款融合骰子机制与古老神秘传说的Roguelike卡牌游戏，带你走进一场惊悚又沉浸的冒险之旅。游戏特色包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 受H.P. 洛夫克拉夫特作品启发的诡异阴森剧情；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 用骰子代替传统魔力值，在控制混沌的同时与运气博弈；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 每一局都有海量不同构筑路线与策略选择，百玩不厌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/b96feaf9928b90b74fa03e70c07f74e1.avif?t=1768212087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras_big/b96feaf9928b90b74fa03e70c07f74e1.avif?t=1768212087 width=1600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/a11aedb502d4f99ce3ea373b34480664.poster.avif?t=1768212087\" width=950 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/a11aedb502d4f99ce3ea373b34480664.webm?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/a11aedb502d4f99ce3ea373b34480664.mp4?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这款游戏中，骰子至高无上！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掷出骰子来激活卡牌和施放法术——祈求好运吧，希望命运站在你这一边！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/3022319a9a45a7f628672b6bfce44d36.avif?t=1768212087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras_big/3022319a9a45a7f628672b6bfce44d36.avif?t=1768212087 width=1600 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/47fe7fa8c3d002f46794683f1544c1c8.poster.avif?t=1768212087\" width=954 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/47fe7fa8c3d002f46794683f1544c1c8.webm?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3095820/extras/47fe7fa8c3d002f46794683f1544c1c8.mp4?t=1768212087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>盒中封印着一个渴望自由的存在</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被遗忘的遗迹深处，主角们偶然发现了一个布满神秘符号的古老盒子。它被沉重的锁链紧紧缠绕，周围满是警示标志，仿佛在阻止某个古老存在挣脱封印，保护世界不被其侵蚀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于这个盒子的传说早已广为流传，但人们始终认为那不过是吓唬小孩的童话罢了。只是……真相似乎比任何传说都更加古老，也更加可怕。</p>",
